{"tid":1671601,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"本地藍絲中小企老細刻意炒黃絲","createTime":"2019-10-23T14:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T15:52:47.000Z","uid":229598,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"52548b924a811ff120d5865c0ebb066132501e76","tid":1671601,"uid":229598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T14:50:31.000Z","msg":"幾日前，同一班本地藍絲中小企(非門市)老細食飯，佢地稱會專炒黃絲伙記，同埋唔會請近呢幾年畢業的大學生。我心裡想，如果有人將呢D藍絲中小企記住，邊個懷疑自己因為黃絲身份而比人炒就記錄。留作歷史記錄。將來光復時，隨時唱《願榮光歸香港》扮自己支持黃絲，同以前瑤日本國旗迎接皇軍一樣咁屁弗鬼。"},{"pid":"d1a94e4ca7e307d13527b7d8727c476f3b0590f9","tid":1671601,"uid":14494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"炒左仲要唔請新人, 做死自己 <br />\n腦細的確腦細<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43b222fa7a2525efd3caf20a3b13a68e417f68d","tid":1671601,"uid":308414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T14:54:30.000Z","msg":"唔開名等咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994a3896d2c371a921c4513f607e7778fd7f4c32","tid":1671601,"uid":310311,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T14:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />後生九成黃絲,然後又唔請大學生,咁即係公司得返一批中坑同廢老?咁生意一定好好啦"},{"pid":"c6cd982fe3d33fb5d0bd26e5e2f3dbe19279e3a1","tid":1671601,"uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T14:58:02.000Z","msg":"你唔請fresh grad 點壓價呀"},{"pid":"01022a1c6c87248eb6d2b0b0b1068062915b9c89","tid":1671601,"uid":256142,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T14:58:51.000Z","msg":"終於搵到呢排中小企倒閉潮既原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd021cc294c1d11f015b3f5f3ec90603fc20a0bc","tid":1671601,"uid":238920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:01:18.000Z","msg":"我專請後生仔,越黃越好,越黃越升得快<br />\n上埋前線代表份人勇於承擔,更加可貴"},{"pid":"0a5ccd